{"word":"ἀχαριστέω","slug":"ἀχαριστέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀχαριστέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <a href='S:ἀχάριστος'><el>ἀχάριστος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be thankless, shew ingratitude</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>= <el>οὐ χαρίζομαι</el>, <i>to discourage</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>;<p/></div>"}]}